ost distant $\\gamma$-ray\nblazar, BZQ J1430+4204 (z = 4.72). Finally, two new $\\gamma$-ray blazars at\nredshifts of z = 3.63 and z = 3.11 are unambiguously detected via very\nsignificant (TS > 25) flares in individual monthly time bins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Sep 2020 21:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
