FD) model can be computed more\nefficiently.\n  (iv) We present an algorithm for computing the two-dimensional channel along\nwhich water flows using Manning's equation; a widely used empirical equation\nthat relates the flow-rate of water in an open channel to the geometry of the\nchannel along with the height of water in the channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 02:08:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
