vertheless, rIGA improves the accuracy of every eigenpair of the\nfirst $N_0$ eigenvalues and eigenfunctions. Here, we allow $N_0$ to be as large\nas the total number of eigenmodes of the original maximum-continuity IGA\ndiscretization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 09:21:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
