isation of $k^a$ and also $k^a$ need not be hypersurface orthogonal. In\naddition, here any particular dynamical equation for metric is not being\nexplicitly used and therefore we feel that our results are solely based on the\nproperties of the null surface.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 11:50:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 03:01:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-29"}
