so enthalpic barriers of\nformation over TiO$_2$-terminated surfaces, or removal of H$_2$ molecules from\nthe PbO-terminated surface.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 11:55:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
