 the\nmGTPase, gives rise to a family of steady states parametrized by the inactive\ntGTPase concentrations. Our findings reveal that the coupling of these two\ndifferent GTPase motifs can dramatically change their steady state behaviors\nand shed light on how such coupling may impact information processing in\neukaryotic cells.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Sep 2020 15:09:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-18"}
